{"tid":891250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"PTT：五毛喜歡偽裝成台灣人唱衰台灣","createTime":"2018-11-06T02:28:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T07:41:25.000Z","uid":152476,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"75d116e0d0b2b7b67c81ec33249640cc2331b2dc","tid":891250,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:28:13.000Z","msg":"各位大大安安呀，最近ptt上五毛愈來愈多大家有目共睹，但大多數五毛只喜歡躲在暗處<br />\n裝台灣人，像realcn這種敢大方承認的五毛已經愈來愈少了，前一陣子捉到了幾個，像是<br />\n一直說台灣觀光景點找不到廁所，中國廁所開始有自動沖水好先進，問他去那找不到廁所<br />\n，只會說一些還真的只有外國觀光客會去的點。要不然就是支那武器番號如數家珍，不論<br />\n跟他說美軍有什麼現有裝備，他都能馬上回答，我們家的XXX有最新的設計，結論一定是<br />\n超英趕美，性能等同或是超越美國裝備，然後再丟給你「不然....OOOXXX」的反問句。<br />\n像此類的笨拙統戰話術就算是小學生也看懂你是誰了，大方承認自己就是來搞統戰的，說<br />\n不定會得到更多掌聲，，為何又打死不肯承認自己是五毛？有沒有八卦呀？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1528650600.A.EA8.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1528650600.A.EA8.html&d=%2FDbU59RiNU1FRFg6cnXZpm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f0efd10d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1528650600.A.EA8.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有點腦都知道五毛文跟五毛推文變多了<br />\n<br />\n9.2還是少數人，但大量的五毛ID卻偽裝台灣人唱衰台灣<br />\n<br />\n很典型例子就是只要有關台灣這國家怎樣的文章，就有五毛ID推文說台灣不是國家<br />\n<br />\n我想92%台灣人以上都會認為台灣是國家<br />\n<br />\n哪來那麼多人自認不是國家？就是對岸五毛阿<br />\n<br />\n敵國網軍裝台灣人唱衰貶低台灣，這是牠們的事情，但放任這種事不是很荒謬嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1525138634.A.A19.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1525138634.A.A19.html&d=%2FDbU59RiNU1FRFg6cnXZpm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=780d03e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1525138634.A.A19.html</a>"},{"pid":"0333bab48e8ca9f50f8b0c0e00a0e8d48dbc2884","tid":891250,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T02:36:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/a7sdGPl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fa7sdGPl.jpg&h=cb763445&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1536340670.A.F93.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1536340670.A.F93.html&d=%2FDbU59RiNU1FRFg6cnXZpm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=22bbdc63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1536340670.A.F93.html</a>"},{"pid":"e4f80994a2bcd3777d60f59fcc6c0b7f3fa325dc","tid":891250,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T03:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72648ee3a4b61a00b7b2773fb2ac88bdf9833309","tid":891250,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T03:51:25.000Z","msg":"網軍"},{"pid":"246e9538464b2a83660a74a890c0dee67059667e","tid":891250,"uid":23023,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T03:52:45.000Z","msg":"連登都有好多踩港撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺明五毛黎<br />\n但係都會有一堆人去附和<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cf7b951b81bce0dacf2ede2ea6a0e6e42272fb","tid":891250,"uid":32699,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"246e9538464b2a83660a74a890c0dee67059667e","tid":891250,"uid":23023,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T03:52:45.000Z","msg":"連登都有好多踩港撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺明五毛黎<br />\n但係都會有一堆人去附和<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T03:56:47.000Z","msg":"仲有一堆台灣分化post<br />\n明明都係果邊啲五毛開post轉貼過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25b448dcc23042efad28ef75acfd000825ad95e","tid":891250,"uid":200834,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T03:57:29.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過其實成個連登淨係得五毛 冇香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n包括樓主<img src=\"/